max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（1）《关于建立职业院校教学工作诊断与改进制度的通知》（教职成厅〔2015〕 2 号）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（2）教育部关于印发《高等职业院校内部质量保证体系诊断与改进指导方 案（试行）》（教职成司函[2015]168 号）&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（3）《关于全面推进职业院校教学工作诊断与改进制度建设的通知》(教职 成司函〔2017〕56 号)&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（4）《江西省高等职业院校内部质量保证体系诊断与改进工作执行方案》 （赣教职成字〔2016〕24 号）</span></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 30px; display: inline-block;"><img data-ratio="1.0813397129186604" data-type="gif" data-w="836" data-width="100%" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEJ2v45mLw2RICEq4RdI01cQJsW0IwGq1qkQaiaKYgKa2h8Qx0vsjKHFCMwevfSSx7PNiaaQV1EnOvyQ/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-original-style="vertical-align: inherit;width: 100%;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;" data-index="5" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEJ2v45mLw2RICEq4RdI01cQJsW0IwGq1qkQaiaKYgKa2h8Qx0vsjKHFCMwevfSSx7PNiaaQV1EnOvyQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" class="__bg_gif" _width="100%" data-order="3" alt="图片" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: inherit; width: 30px !important; display: block; visibility: visible !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 5px 1em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(76, 162, 254), rgb(76, 162, 254));"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !i